蛇，求入group @funghk510<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我果幾版<br />\n盧點出山"},{"pid":"be4bf094a4e0d6059a361ad5eaad3e3e6eb379a1","tid":146523,"uid":4957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T09:25:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e439fc8598cd6c4ee5898fe1d6a1463fa51bebe","tid":146523,"uid":38234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T09:29:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d42c5838252b020e955c446cae2328b85b0733a6","tid":146523,"uid":84513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T09:41:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>支持盧蛇手足去哂邊</blockquote><br />\n支持盧蛇，求入group @funghk510<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我果幾版<br />\n盧點出山</blockquote><br />\n盧今晚有水嗎？準備出五場早水嗎？<br />\n每晚，若不贏四場，你還算盧蛇嗎？<br />\n<br />\n*真想跟你去買，你每天揀的波<br />\n我每日中幾場，這算是厲害<br />\n為何無論我，智商怎樣高<br />\n怎樣也不可贏多你一場(怎樣也沒令自己去爭勝)<br />\n<br />\n難道看盤看太多，看到自己confuse左<br />\n試圖去亂鳩買，度波有咩撚用<br />\n不懂得如何看盤口，還是我猜不透，莊家真正的心意<br />\n<br />\n成日即場買角大，即刻停角半個鐘<br />\n車路士正仆街，曼聯都冚家剷<br />\n角球，成日半七全九，全班正仆街，夾埋玩鳩我*<br />\n<br />\n盧 真係好鬼勁 日德意法西全都中<br />\n可是沒出水比我，有甚麼撚野用？<br />\n<br />\n難道看盤看太多，看到自己confuse左<br />\n試圖去亂鳩買，度波有咩撚用<br />\n不懂得如何看盤口，還是我猜不透，莊家真正的心意<br />\n<br />\n成日即場買角大，即刻停角半個鐘<br />\n望住佢地鳩猜，我真係把幾火<br />\n若封盤 角大再次高水 我可能仲係 買多次角大<br />\n盧蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3de1aa606ea735b2e0e14a25cd19eeefb696c93","tid":146523,"uid":38234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T09:42:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ee896e34859183aeee9ca7f977ad6226bd0487f","tid":146523,"uid":400